e":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"詳情係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c015c5cfeb641f3d299fdb09940153c9a72875","tid":2071782,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"白頭佬根本一 d 抗爭意志都冇<br />\n出份糧架咋，靠佢就含得撚"},{"pid":"67a43c820ba16456cd72267363d8a85a682d5e74","tid":2071782,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"604d37b1ad6a2a3a6ec701b011b44d900666d7fa","tid":2071782,"uid":360975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"食屎啦白頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拒選立會主席搞到大口狗上台一鑊仲唔夠甘？提香港人記住你幾撚仆街？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rs4RmO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rs4RmO.png&h=724abae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m5xwwmX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm5xwwmX.png&h=c377bd93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補source <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200619/7N64DTKEIXY4GLHGRGGJSCKNZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200619%2F7N64DTKEIXY4GLHGRGGJSCKNZU%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2ww9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=246003e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200619%2F7N64DTKEIXY4GLHGRGGJSCKNZU%2F&h=6874c003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200619/7N64DTKEIXY4GLHGRGGJSCKNZU/</a> <br />\n輸唔起就咪玩啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"066b8ab1a24d737931efdba272fed624d673fbf6","tid":2071782,"uid":64273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16f7b209ddd3b23eca2d49090796bf7f9191c032","tid":2071782,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4196e1e503e4781d1b9d50d72b909133e22e8e79","tid":2071782,"uid":252659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73fcee7f54f418e7537c6dfd6bafd7e8ecaa97f3","tid":2071782,"uid":105340,"like":174,"dislike":2,"score":172,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"白頭佬ON9架<br />\n有立法會主席唔做 配合阿爺劇本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:27:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾飯民<br />\n邊個投佢真係要自殺"},{"pid":"39163c020a1fbb8e0bbf3f5625abbf67440f16a0","tid":2071782,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5044766d984200002730320f2959c2491967b30b","tid":2071782,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:53:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">血淚實錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：就係個白頭佬+新西肥仔搞散咗我人生第一次工潮!!!!!!!!!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我係港航受害員工，港航無錢然後炒撚左一班員工，我地搞左一場好撚失敗既工潮，由幾百人、上晒新聞既行動，變成得番廿條人、無人知發生咩事既「工潮」。<br />\n<br />\n嗱，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">話晒係航空業，梗係搵吳敏兒同譚文豪</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[size=5]，但係有同事好撚堅持要搵埋<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">街工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>，又<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大讚白頭佬👨🏻&zwj;🦳</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算啦，諗住多個幫手都好，但咁就high high左😭😭😭<br />\n<br />\n但有個叫Tracy既同事成鳩日話要搵白頭佬，又安排大家去葵芳街工聽意見。<br />\n<br />\n開頭都幾有聲勢既，一心諗住會唔會爭取到好既成果，但點知搞搞下好唔對路，Core發言人唔見左，吳敏兒同譚文豪都唔見埋，得返街工人，屌，就係嗰條新西肥仔。原來Tracy就係新西肥仔條女，個八婆日鳩日屌鳩話譚文豪、吳敏兒離棄咗大家。我地成班友勁燥，以為真係被背叛。點知原來係街工同條八婆合謀，所有野都唔通知譚、吳，自把自為、自以為是，趕撚走晒啲做得野既人。<br />\n<br />\n其實中間whatsapp group出現咗一輪罵戰，有同事質疑點解無啦啦唔見咗吳敏兒同譚文豪，質疑係咪tracy佢哋玩排擠，所以比較親職工盟既人都唔見晒⋯<br />\n<br />\n有人提出質疑，但原來唔係core team就表達吓疑問都會比人屌返轉頭⋯咁後來都好無癮，又有啲好似工潮大勢已去咁⋯過多排又話白頭佬安排咗去勞工處，搞搞吓總之訴求就最後全部落空⋯<br />\n<br />\n本來都已經搵到工、工潮玩撚完，放棄咗，[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">點知尋日睇街工記招，參選名單排第一竟然又係個仆街肥仔盧藝賢+白頭⋯</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">真相大白，為選舉插手港航工潮，我哋輸到渣都冇，你地就贏左我哋啲相做你哋既競選政績呀👍🏻</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">做勞工運動出賣勞工</span></span>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">做議員就讓位俾建制</span></span>、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做民主運動就率先放棄初選</span></span>，真係屌晒你地老母含家0👎🏻<br />\n<br />\n留名睇所有參選人被DQ，賣港街工四席全入🤗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3Lqzqe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3Lqzqe.jpg&h=75f1e27f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nCaption：最初行動有吳敏兒譚文豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/euD7NLp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeuD7NLp.jpg&h=dcaa1e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCaption：右一就係「梁耀忠右轉世靈童」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ag4Oxcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAg4Oxcq.jpg&h=489d7708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boGJk5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FboGJk5K.jpg&h=58c44b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71AaLxr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71AaLxr.jpg&h=5a5ecc6f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFd0oi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFd0oi5.jpg&h=908cdcee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:29:36.000Z","msg":"點解有人仲想白頭佬 白頭佬同譚文豪水平差咁遠都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 某程度上你個同事都傻傻地"},{"pid":"56cb0796c3a0f185dfcda56988c9939a3810d51f","tid":2071782,"uid":211974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a1cebcaa17a88d8bb97280c807791f53fcf1bf5","tid":2071782,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bc01675cb190280c7bd202ed3d741bb0c60b47","tid":2071782,"uid":304306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:40:22.000Z","msg":"提早證明35+係廢話啫 <img src=\"/asse